reviewText: The quality of the recording leaves a considerable amount to be desired.  Still worth having if you are a fan.

This is one of the best live proformances on the market today. For those who like Nancy Wilson, you will be glued to your seat the entire show. Everything she does on this disc is absolutely fantastic. I have never seen a performance that great none-stop, from beginning to end, Nancy is "simply great." Take it one who knows.
